Package application.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BackendException
    An Exception unique to this project
    InvalidAdministratorException
    Exception that when thrown means that a User with a authLevel less than 2 has appeared when there shouldn't have
    InvalidItemException
    Exception that when thrown means that a Item with that doesn't exist appeared when there shouldn't have
    InvalidListException
    Exception that when thrown means that a List was not in an expected format
    InvalidLocationException
    Exception that when thrown means that a Locations was used inappropriately
    InvalidSessionException
    Exception that when thrown means that a Session with an incorrect format has appeared when there shouldn't have
    InvalidTokenException
    Exception that when thrown means that a Token with either an invalid authenticator or with an expiration greater than system.currentTime was used
    InvalidUserException
    Exception that when thrown means that a User with an invalid format has appeared when there shouldn't have
